# User stories

- As the game designer, I frequently add, modify or remove ships in the game. I'll want to store these changes in the app. 
 
- As the game designer, when I'm doing balancing work, I want to inspect the characteristics of the ships and compare them to each other. 

- As a playtester, I want to access a list of ships for a quick reference of their characteristics. For this I want to be able to restrict my search by faction.

- As a playtester, I want to compare the characteristics of two ships when I'm selecting my fleet in the game.
